{"tid":2059010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【死黑警又老屈系列】前空姐被指以雷射光襲警受審 辯方質疑警從沒搜出雷射筆","createTime":"2020-06-10T14:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T08:20:52.000Z","uid":117837,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"576e80636774e95e79b2bdf04ade5fb382e47d74","tid":2059010,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T14:41:53.000Z","msg":"辯方又指，無論是被告被捕時、抑或是事後帶返警署搜身，警方都沒有從被告身上搜出雷射筆；而呈堂雷射筆與現場檢獲的雷射筆長度不一，質疑兩者並非同一支。<br />\n⋯<br />\n事發時駐守油麻地特遣隊兼任西九龍應應變大隊第二梯隊的<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>朱冠強</strong></span></span>稱，去年8月10日晚上與同袍在尖沙嘴彌敦道築起防線。<br />\n⋯<br />\n朱續供稱，此時50名較溫和示威者行至警方防線5至10米外，原本已停止照射雷射筆；但突然有一道綠色雷射光線從該批示威者中射出，射向他的左眼及鼻子。雖然射向他左眼的雷射光「少於一秒」，但他已感到眼前一白，「當時冇痛，但有流眼水」。<br />\n⋯<br />\n朱強調，由首次被雷射光照射、鎖定女方身份直至制服她，「佢冇離開我視線」。對於警方聲稱該女子在地上爬時仍拿著雷射筆，但從被告身上或手上卻找不到雷射筆，朱解釋：「當時有好多示威者用雨傘襲擊我哋，情況混亂，我睇唔到支雷射筆幾時離開佢隻手。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://thumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub/h3ATHxTUif6pG3e0uIHkfT8wBrM=/arc-photo-appledaily/ap-ne-1-prod/public/EPNTJLYEIAKS4IHAARRM45ZMFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub%2Fh3ATHxTUif6pG3e0uIHkfT8wBrM%3D%2Farc-photo-appledaily%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FEPNTJLYEIAKS4IHAARRM45ZMFA.jpg&h=51123f4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n證人警員朱冠強。（黃耀興攝）<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200610/WA3ZKHORMBEWMIGOKZCLPPRDSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200610%2FWA3ZKHORMBEWMIGOKZCLPPRDSY%2F&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRHpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=1ddeb508\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200610%2FWA3ZKHORMBEWMIGOKZCLPPRDSY%2F&h=316a0e3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200610/WA3ZKHORMBEWMIGOKZCLPPRDSY/</a>"},{"pid":"95588404397d68d03308924ef61b0e9c193af614","tid":2059010,"uid":117837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T14:54:10.000Z","msg":"死黑警又屈又砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc701d0b2b85ea6d6a65bf66e9d6097f64eb1ca","tid":2059010,"uid":117837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T14:59:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>朱冠強</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3126a089e6dcfc2776458c6b516ecc3fbae9f2fb","tid":2059010,"uid":155936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:00:42.000Z","msg":"又一單搜唔到野都擺明老屈"},{"pid":"895e06c124a095e48d5b2d4397c1005285718bda","tid":2059010,"uid":132587,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:00:59.000Z","msg":"比你搞到工都無埋仲要屈鳩人<br />\n你係咪男人黎架<br />\n做狗做到咁撚賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf4b0ea212b50a1d4922e2f0f0a33fb39671648","tid":2059010,"uid":149092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:02:12.000Z","msg":"有名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c82266f6e0e2352a91e9870acb4cb1e1d249a06","tid":2059010,"uid":20688,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:09:11.000Z","msg":"比人射住隻眼，但「佢冇離開我視線」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7d82c87da50ea3e64fd8813f36fa173a1a849d","tid":2059010,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:09:42.000Z","msg":"當大家仲係度內鬥嘅時候，麻煩你睇下流亡台灣嘅手足點講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2059034\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2059034</a>"},{"pid":"84ac1ae97cda2cd52b5e89f5b33c834ec03d867c","tid":2059010,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:12:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f89ac0ff49c4422002